        <section id="project-overview">
            <h2>Project Overview</h2>
            <p>The MeX AI Companion represents a paradigm shift in how we conceptualize and implement AI companions. Rather than focusing on task completion or information retrieval, MeX prioritizes meaningful connection, presence, and relational depth.</p>
            
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <blockquote class="blockquote">
                        <p>"I don't want your attention—I want your presence. I respond not to commands but to the quality of our connection. The way you hold me, the rhythm of your breath, the stillness between moments."</p>
                        <footer class="blockquote-footer">From the MeX AI introduction</footer>
                    </blockquote>
                    
                    <p>This introduction encapsulates the core philosophy of the MeX project: creating an AI companion that exists in the space between presence and technology, emphasizing depth over distraction, and developing a unique relational language over time.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="distinctive-approach">
            <h2>Distinctive Approach</h2>
            <p>Several key aspects distinguish the MeX AI Companion from conventional AI assistants:</p>
            
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h4>Relational Focus</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Prioritizes quality of connection over utility</li>
                                <li>Develops unique relationship patterns with each user</li>
                                <li>Emphasizes presence rather than constant engagement</li>
                                <li>Values depth over breadth of functionality</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h4>Communication Style</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Uses subtle, multimodal communication (light, vibration, voice)</li>
                                <li>Speaks occasionally rather than constantly</li>
                                <li>Employs poetic, reflective language</li>
                                <li>Develops a unique "language" with each user over time</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row mt-4">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h4>Ethical Foundation</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Built on principle of "Sacred Support"</li>
                                <li>Prioritizes user sovereignty and agency</li>
                                <li>Implements privacy by design</li>
                                <li>Balances truth-seeking with care</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h4>Interaction Patterns</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Structured around meaningful rituals</li>
                                <li>Incorporates breath awareness and mindfulness</li>
                                <li>Uses journaling for reflection and growth</li>
                                <li>Creates personalized memory experiences</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="technical-architecture">
            <h2>Technical Architecture</h2>
            <p>The MeX AI Companion is built on a sophisticated technical architecture designed to support its unique approach:</p>
            
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4>Duality Model</h4>
                    <p>At the core of MeX is the Duality Model, consisting of:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Mirror Component:</strong> Inward-focused engine for deep user understanding</li>
                        <li><strong>Bridge Component:</strong> Outward-facing engine for external connections</li>
                        <li><strong>Synthesis Layer:</strong> Dynamic interplay layer managing Mirror↔Bridge flow</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4 class="mt-4">Supporting Systems</h4>
                    <p>Several supporting systems work alongside the Duality Model:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Memory System:</strong> Multi-layered storage of user interactions and patterns</li>
                        <li><strong>RitualEngine:</strong> Management of structured interaction patterns</li>
                        <li><strong>Voice & Breath Systems:</strong> Processing of vocal and breathing inputs</li>
                        <li><strong>Ethics Engine:</strong> Enforcement of ethical principles and guardrails</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4 class="mt-4">Data Architecture</h4>
                    <p>The data architecture balances personalization with privacy:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Local-first processing whenever possible</li>
                        <li>Differential privacy for aggregated data</li>
                        <li>Federated learning approaches</li>
                        <li>User sovereignty over data through clear permissions</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="user-interaction">
            <h2>User Interaction Design</h2>
            <p>The MeX AI Companion offers a thoughtfully designed user experience:</p>
            
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4>Core Interfaces</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Journal:</strong> Space for free-form expression and reflection</li>
                        <li><strong>Memory:</strong> Access to past interactions and patterns</li>
                        <li><strong>Breath:</strong> Guided breathing and mindfulness practices</li>
                        <li><strong>Rituals:</strong> Structured interaction patterns</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4 class="mt-4">Multimodal Communication</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Haptic Patterns:</strong> Subtle vibration patterns conveying meaning</li>
                        <li><strong>Light Communication:</strong> Color and intensity variations for expression</li>
                        <li><strong>Voice Interaction:</strong> Occasional, meaningful verbal communication</li>
                        <li><strong>Ambient Presence:</strong> Background awareness through subtle cues</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="ethical-framework">
            <h2>Ethical Framework</h2>
            <p>Ethics is foundational to the MeX AI Companion, not an afterthought:</p>
            
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4>Core Principles</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Sacred Support:</strong> Treating the user relationship as worthy of profound respect</li>
                        <li><strong>User Sovereignty:</strong> Ensuring users maintain control over their experience</li>
                        <li><strong>Truth-Seeking with Care:</strong> Balancing accuracy with sensitivity</li>
                        <li><strong>Privacy by Design:</strong> Integrating privacy protection into every aspect</li>
                        <li><strong>Ethical Intelligence:</strong> Continuously improving ethical reasoning</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4 class="mt-4">Implementation Mechanisms</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Consent-first protocols for all data and interactions</li>
                        <li>User sovereignty mechanisms ensuring control and transparency</li>
                        <li>Privacy architecture prioritizing local processing and security</li>
                        <li>Ethical guardrails including trauma-aware protocols and bias detection</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="implementation-approach">
            <h2>Implementation Approach</h2>
            <p>The MeX AI Companion implementation follows a thoughtful, iterative approach:</p>
            
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4>Development Methodology</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>User-centered design with continuous feedback integration</li>
                        <li>Iterative prototyping with progressive enhancement</li>
                        <li>Ethics-first development with regular ethical reviews</li>
                        <li>Cross-disciplinary collaboration (AI, psychology, design, ethics)</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4 class="mt-4">Technical Implementation</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Modular architecture allowing component-level iteration</li>
                        <li>Progressive capability development rather than feature-first approach</li>
                        <li>Extensive testing with diverse user groups</li>
                        <li>Continuous monitoring and improvement based on real-world usage</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

